         <div class="content">
          <section class="block-hms-mods-content system_main_block" id="block-hms-mods-content">
           <article about="/executive-education-0" class="mode--full landing_page" data-history-node-id="35" id="node-35" role="article">
            <div class="row landing-page-content">
             <div class="columns small-12">
              <h1 class="node-title hide-title">
               <span class="field-wrapper">
                Executive Education
               </span>
              </h1>
             </div>
             <div>
              <h3 class="columns intro-subtitle field__item">
               Health care is dynamic and complex, and it impacts wide-reaching aspects of the global economy
              </h3>
              <div class="field-wrapper body field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__items">
               <div class="columns small-12 medium-8 field__item">
                <p>
                 In the U.S. alone, spending is projected to reach nearly 20% of GDP by 2020. Business leaders are recognizing that success in this rapidly evolving marketplace requires a fundamental understanding of current medical practices, the changing economic landscape of health care and the latest advances in biomedical science.
                </p>
                <p>
                 For more than 200 years, Harvard Medical School (HMS) has shaped the design of medical school education throughout the world while preparing generations of physicians for leadership roles in patient care, education, research and policy.
                </p>
                <h5>
                 Now, HMS is bringing its expertise to organizations that seek to drive growth and innovation in health care.
                </h5>
                <ul>
                </ul>
               </div>
              </div>
              <div class="columns small-12 field-wrapper field field--name-field-cta-link field--type-link field--label-hidden field__items">
               <div class="component-button field__item">
                <a href="/about-us/contact-us">
                 Interested in learning more? Contact us.
                </a>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="view-mode-full">
             <div class="field-wrapper field field--name-field-components field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
              <div class="field__item">
               <div class="bundle--card_navigation_component paragraph paragraph--type--card-navigation-component paragraph--view-mode--default">
                <div class="row">
                 <div class="columns small-12 medium-8 sidebar-full">
                  <h2 class="component-title field__item">
                   Learning Options
                  </h2>
                 </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row small-up-1 medium-up-3 field-wrapper field field--name-field-card-navigation-item field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
                 <div class="bundle--card_navigation_item columns block-link paragraph paragraph--type--card-navigation-item paragraph--view-mode--default">
                  <div class="title-text-content field__item">
                   <article about="/custom-programs" class="mode--title_text basic_inner_page" data-history-node-id="30" id="node-30" role="article">
                    <h2 class="node-title">
                     <a href="/custom-programs" rel="bookmark">
                      <span class="field-wrapper">
                       Custom Programs
                      </span>
                     </a>
                    </h2>
                    <div class="view-mode-title_text">
                     <div class="field-wrapper field field--name-field-teaser-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__items">
                      <div class="field__item">
                       <p>
                        Our customized executive programs equip industry professionals with the knowledge required to create value in a complex and changing health care landscape.
                       </p>
                      </div>
                     </div>
                    </div>
                   </article>
                  </div>
                  <p class="button-cta field-wrapper field field--name-field-cta-text field--type-string field--label-hidden field__items">
                   <span class="field__item">
                    LEARN MORE
                   </span>
                  </p>
                 </div>
                 <div class="bundle--card_navigation_item columns block-link paragraph paragraph--type--card-navigation-item paragraph--view-mode--default">
                  <div class="title-text-content field__item">
                   <article about="/open-enrollment" class="mode--title_text basic_inner_page" data-history-node-id="31" id="node-31" role="article">
                    <h2 class="node-title">
                     <a href="/open-enrollment" rel="bookmark">
                      <span class="field-wrapper">
                       Open Enrollment
                      </span>
                     </a>
                    </h2>
                    <div class="view-mode-title_text">
                     <div class="field-wrapper field field--name-field-teaser-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__items">
                      <div class="field__item">
                       <p>
                        Focused programs delivering breakthrough research, new perspectives, and actionable insights.
                       </p>
                       <p>
                       </p>
                      </div>
                     </div>
                    </div>
                   </article>
                  </div>
                  <p class="button-cta field-wrapper field field--name-field-cta-text field--type-string field--label-hidden field__items">
